meta_marketplace_product_description:
The McDavid ankle support is a sportsman's best friend. Almost all of us have suffered a small or serious ankle injury at some time, and what bothers us most is not being able to practice our favourite sport. Thanks to the new functions of this sports ankle brace you can continue to enjoy any activity. Its lightweight but firm design helps stabilize your foot and prevent possible sprains or help with your recovery.

We have focused on safety and comfort first and foremost. Its lightweight design consists of a thin single-layer polyester fabric that makes the ankle brace perfect for sports such as basketball, volleyball, handball or tennis. Due to its extra thin design, the McDavid ankle bracelet fits perfectly in most (sports) shoes.

McDavid Ankle Support

  • Made of one-layer polyester fabric for full support and minimum weight.
  • The design simulates the athletic tape with the strapping pattern in figure 8.
  • Superior compression belt for a personalized fit.
  • Latex-free neoprene provides thermal compression.
  • Fully adjustable without untying or removing the shoe.
  • Padded lining and reinforced zips.
meta_marketplace_product_description_de: Die McDavid 195 Knöchelbandage mit Riemen bietet eine hervorragende Knöchelunterstützung zur Vorbeugung und Heilung von Knöchelverstauchungen und -verletzungen. Diese leichte Knöchelbandage bietet eine schnelle und einfache Alternative zu den traditionell bei Verstauchungen und anderen Knöchelverletzungen verwendeten Taping-Techniken. Die McDavid UltraLight Laced Ankle Brace (195) kann Ihren Knöchel stützen, weitere Schäden verhindern und die Schmerzen Ihrer Verletzung lindern. Die perfekte Unterstützung für Sportarten wie Basketball, Volleyball, Handball, Hockey, Tennis oder jede andere Sportart mit viel horizontaler Bewegung.
meta_marketplace_product_description_fr: L'emblématique chevillère McDavid 195 renforcée avec bandes strap offre un superbe soutien de la cheville pour prévenir et soigner les entorses et les blessures. La chevillère à lacets ultra légère McDavid (195) peut soutenir votre cheville, prévenir d'autres blessure et aider à soulager la douleur de l'entorse. C'est le support idéal pour les sports comme le basket-ball, le volley-ball, le handball, le hockey, le tennis ou tout autre sport comportant beaucoup de déplacements latéraux.
meta_marketplace_product_description_nl: De McDavid 195 Enkelbrace met riemen biedt een uitstekende ondersteuning van de enkel ter voorkoming en genezing van verstuikingen en verwondingen. De McDavid UltraLight Laced Ankle Brace (195) kan uw enkel ondersteunen, verdere schade voorkomen en de pijn van uw blessure verlichten. De perfecte ondersteuning voor sporten als basketbal, volleybal, handbal, hockey, tennis of elke andere sport met veel horizontale beweging.

meta_marketplace_product_description:
The McDavid ankle support is a sportsman's best friend. Almost all of us have suffered a small or serious ankle injury at some time, and what bothers us most is not being able to practice our favourite sport. Thanks to the new functions of this sports ankle brace you can continue to enjoy any activity. Its lightweight but firm design helps stabilize your foot and prevent possible sprains or help with your recovery.

We have focused on safety and comfort first and foremost. Its lightweight design consists of a thin single-layer polyester fabric that makes the ankle brace perfect for sports such as basketball, volleyball, handball or tennis. Due to its extra thin design, the McDavid ankle bracelet fits perfectly in most (sports) shoes.

McDavid Ankle Support

  • Made of one-layer polyester fabric for full support and minimum weight.

  • Fully adjustable without untying or removing the shoe.
  • Padded lining and reinforced zips.
